short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Phần mềm InEcom hỗ trợ đặt đơn nhanh

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Tool for automation marketing for Shopee & Tiktok - Ecommerce Marketplace

1. Automation Checkout
- Auto add to cart
- Auto change quantity 
- Auto check out in shopee
- Auto send order id to shopee
- Auto sync order history

2. Automation Check Stock
- Auto fetch stock from item of shopee.vn
- Auto fetch ads data from  shopee.vn and tiktok.com
- Auto start flash sale slot for shopee.vn
